title: Prince eSports [OOL] LF Coach
body:
Prince e-Sports is looking for a coach for both its Main Roster and Academy team. Both of these rosters are filled with some of the Amateur scenes most promising players.

Rosters will be provided upon request.

If you are interested please contact either myself, "I am Sleepy" or "Torpid" in client, or go to our website, click on the apply tab and fill in the form.

Past experience is a must, along with good communication skills and a sound understanding of the game.
